Package org.aavso.tools.vstar.ui.dialog.series

Class Summary
AbstractSeriesVisibilityDialog<T extends JPanel> This dialog permits the visibility of plot series to be changed, and allows subclasses to extend its functionality by adding series-related panes and behavior.
MeanSourceDialog This class represents a dialog that builds on the series visibility dialog in order to permit selection of the series that is to be the source of the means series.
MeanSourcePane This class represents a pane with radio buttons showing which series is to be used as the source to create the means series.
SeriesVisibilityDialog This dialog permits the visibility of plot series to be changed.
SeriesVisibilityPane This class represents a pane with checkboxes showing those series that are rendered.
